</p>
			</div>
		</div></li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 198px"><div style="width: 198px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 196px;"><div style="margin:0px auto;"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:CICR_monument_NL_05.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/CICR_monument_NL_05.jpg/294px-CICR_monument_NL_05.jpg" decoding="async" width="196" height="110" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/CICR_monument_NL_05.jpg/441px-CICR_monument_NL_05.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/CICR_monument_NL_05.jpg/587px-CICR_monument_NL_05.jpg 2x" data-file-width="4096" data-file-height="2304" /></a></div></div>
